author: Andy McDonald
title: These Photos Of The Trump Administration Say Pretty Much Everything
text:
These Photos Of The Trump Administration Say Pretty Much Everything And more! By Andy McDonald 
Hey, hear anything interesting out of the White House these days? Yeah, probably not. OK, well, I’ll see you later then ... 
Ha, of course we’re kidding! And when we’re not hearing crazy things, we’re seeing them. 
Once again, photos out of this administration tell us everything. HuffPost Illustration
